<yd-layout>
  <template>
    <!--导航栏-->

      style="border-bottom: 0"
      bgcolor="#3AB07E"
      color="#FFF"
      title="发布资讯"

      <yd-navbar-back-icon slot="left" color="#FFF" @click.native="onPop"
        >返回

      <yd-cell-item>

          placeholder="请输入您的内容"
          v-model="news_con"

      >提交</yd-button
    >
  </template>
</yd-layout>
